      <p><a href="ch61s06.html#MonstersB-C36">Bodaks</a> are the undead remnants of humanoids who have been destroyed by the touch of absolute evil.<a href="img/MonstersB-C.Bodak.jpg" target="_blank"><span class="inlinemediaobject"><img src="thumb/MonstersB-C.Bodak.jpg" align="right"/></span></a></p>
      <p>A <a href="ch61s06.html#MonstersB-C36">bodak</a> retains fleeting memories of its past life and can speak Common (or some other humanoid language).</p>
