          <p><span class="strong"><strong>Death Gaze (Su):</strong></span> Death, range 30 feet, Fortitude DC 15 negates. Humanoids who die from this attack are transformed into <a href="ch61s06.html#MonstersB-C36">bodaks</a> 24 hours later. The save DC is Charisma-based.</p>
