          <a class="indexterm" name="MonstersB-C39"/>
          <p><span class="strong"><strong>Vulnerability to Sunlight (Ex):</strong></span> <a href="ch61s06.html#MonstersB-C36">Bodaks</a> loathe sunlight, for its merest touch burns their impure flesh. Each round of exposure to the direct rays of the sun deals 1 point of damage to the creature.</p>
